] Test response construction (status codes, body format)\n- [ ] Test error handling (4xx/5xx scenarios)\n- [ ] Test edge cases (empty body, oversized payload)\n- [ ] Target: 80%+ coverage\n\n## T-6: reconciler/ — reconciler tests\n\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/*_test.go`\n- [ ] Test state sync (convergence to desired state)\n- [ ] Test retry logic (max retries, backoff, success after retry)\n- [ ] Test idempotency (repeated calls → same result)\n- [ ] Test error propagation (dependency failure handling)\n- [ ] Target: 75%+ coverage\n\n## T-7: Run tests and verify coverage\n\n- [ ] `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` — all tests pass\n- [ ] `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -cover` — coverage meets targets\n- [ ] `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -race` — no race conditions\n- [ ] Fix any failing tests or coverage gaps\n\n---\n\n## Dependency Graph\n\n```\nT-1 ──┬── T-2\n      ├── T-3\n      ├── T-4\n      ├── T-5\n      └── T-6\n\nT-2 ──┐\nT-3 ──┤\nT-4 ──┤\nT-5 ──┤── T-7\nT-6 ──┘\n```\n\n## Parallelizable Groups\n\n| Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n|-------|-------|---------------|\n| G1 | T-1 | None |\n| G2 | T-2, T-3, T-4, T-5, T-6 | T-1 |\n| G3 | T-7 | T-2, T-3, T-4, T-5, T-6 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775886301763,"end":1775886301773}}}}
